     <p class="title">（学习贯彻党的十八届四中全会精神）陈希：提高党员干部法治思维和依法办事能力</p> 
     <p class="info"><span>作者:</span><span>来源:</span><span>更新时间:2014-12-19</span><span>点击次数:<script language="javascript" src="http://www.zgltzyw.org/includes/hits.php?id=1345"></script></span> </p>
